      <title>埃德维斯警告称，印度长期债券交易已变得拥挤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/india-s-long-bonds-have-become-a-crowded-trade-edelweiss-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位印度债券基金经理表示，该国 30 年期债券的涨势已过头，因为交易员夸大了政策利率下调的预期，并且外国基金增加了购买量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/india-s-long-bonds-have-become-a-crowded-trade-edelweiss-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 05:16:22 GMT</pubDate>
